Christine Lampard, 43, has shared a heartfelt tribute to her husband Frank on Instagram as he turned 44. She thanked the former footballer for being the “best husband and daddy”. The couple got married in 2015, and share daughter Patricia, three, and son Freddie, two. Christine is also stepmum to Luna, 16, and Isla, 14, from Frank's romance with model Elen Rivas. Posting a beaming photo of Frank clutching a glass of wine on holiday, Christine wrote: “Wrapping up the birthday celebrations for the best husband and daddy we could wish for! We love you @franklampard”.